data.description: Country living in the city. Look at this secluded, fenced 1/2 acre lot and house with 180 feet on Billy Creek. Take your kayak or canoe and launch from your back yard and make your way downstream to the park or continue to the Caloosahatchee River. Check it out on Google Map. Drive up the beautiful tree lined private dead end road into a quiet island like neighborhood. The house features all new upgrades including roof, AC, electric, plumbing, carpeting, new paint inside and out. The one and half car garage has plenty of room for storage. New construction across the road and great neighbors. Plenty of room for a pool and a barn if you need more space. A must see.
